{"calories":"860","carbs":106,"category":{"badge_name":"","display_name":"Dinner","display_order":1,"is_filterable":false,"insight_segment_slug":"main-recipe-ratings","slug":"main"},"choices_available":[],"description":"\u003cp\u003eTomatoes. Bacon. Pesto. Cheese. Chef Giuseppe is combining some of his favorite flavors into one tasty bowl of pasta. Garlic-roasted tomatoes get tossed with spiral-shaped gemelli noodles (perfect for holding the sauce). It’s topped with crispy mushrooms cooked with hickory barbecue spice mix to emulate the flavors of smoky bacon, and a lemon-infused pesto for a hint of brightness. \u003c/p\u003e","difficulty":"easy","external_id":"80164af9a4","fat":40,"images":[{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/75207/large_cropped_pBcsF68QVWGChXdZhXwi_Roasted_Tomato_Pasta_with_Mushroom__Bacon__and_Lemon_Pesto_007_MAIN.jpg","size":"large_cropped","type":"main_cropped"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/75206/yCiPjh4qQweO27doFHmW_Roasted_Tomato_Pasta_with_Mushroom__Bacon__and_Lemon_Pesto_004_THUMB.jpg","size":"full","type":"card"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/75206/menu_small_yCiPjh4qQweO27doFHmW_Roasted_Tomato_Pasta_with_Mushroom__Bacon__and_Lemon_Pesto_004_THUMB.jpg","size":"medium-rectangle","type":"card"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/75204/8rxRkxL7Q66lWRdS6KHi_Roasted_Tomato_Pasta_with_Mushroom__Bacon__and_Lemon_Pesto_006_HERO.jpg","size":"full","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/75204/hero_8rxRkxL7Q66lWRdS6KHi_Roasted_Tomato_Pasta_with_Mushroom__Bacon__and_Lemon_Pesto_006_HERO.jpg","size":"hero","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/75204/menu_small_8rxRkxL7Q66lWRdS6KHi_Roasted_Tomato_Pasta_with_Mushroom__Bacon__and_Lemon_Pesto_006_HERO.jpg","size":"medium-rectangle","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/75204/small_square_8rxRkxL7Q66lWRdS6KHi_Roasted_Tomato_Pasta_with_Mushroom__Bacon__and_Lemon_Pesto_006_HERO.jpg","size":"small-square","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/75204/medium_square_8rxRkxL7Q66lWRdS6KHi_Roasted_Tomato_Pasta_with_Mushroom__Bacon__and_Lemon_Pesto_006_HERO.jpg","size":"medium-square","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/75204/recipe_profile_page_8rxRkxL7Q66lWRdS6KHi_Roasted_Tomato_Pasta_with_Mushroom__Bacon__and_Lemon_Pesto_006_HERO.jpg","size":"large-rectangle","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/75205/4Q34eo0aQWSdvML5XjAa_Roasted_Tomato_Pasta_with_Mushroom__Bacon__and_Lemon_Pesto_007_MAIN.jpg","size":"full","type":"portrait"}}],"name":"Roasted Tomato Pasta with Mushroom “Bacon” and Lemon Pesto","novice_time":null,"portion_count":2,"prep_time":"30-40","pro_time":null,"product_type":{"slug":"subscription","included_in_subscription":true},"protein":30,"public_slug":"roasted-tomato-pasta-with-mushroom-bacon-and-lemon-pesto","pdf_url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/public_uploads/recipe/region_schedule/downloadable_recipe_card/56865/recipe_card20190726-10-1sisaf3.pdf","recipe_id":7774,"type":"regular","servings":2,"short_name":"Roasted Tomato Pasta","subtitle":"with Mushroom “Bacon” and Lemon Pesto","title":"Roasted Tomato Pasta","legal_copy_short":null,"available_for_non_sub":false,"additional_price":"0","cooking_tip":"\u003cp\u003eBe sure to read through the entire recipe before you begin cooking. Trust us—you\u0026#x27;ll be glad you did!\u003c/p\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cp\u003eWiping mushrooms clean instead of rinsing prevents them from absorbing water. They won\u0026#x27;t brown well if they\u0026#x27;re too wet.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe skin of the lemon (and other citrus fruits) is home to the highest concentration of aromatic oils, so chefs use zest to add bright flavor and a little texture. It\u0026#x27;s easier and safer to zest the lemon before cutting and juicing.\u003c/p\u003e","equipment":["10\" large pot","baking sheet"],"id":7774,"ingredients":["oyster mushrooms","garlic","hickory barbecue spice mix","grape tomatoes","gemelli","lemon","basil","pesto","shaved Parmesan cheese","8\" aluminum tin"],"ingredients_full":[{"name":"oyster mushrooms","quantity":"6.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":1,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/609/medium_square_oyster-mushrooms.jpg"},{"name":"garlic","quantity":"2.0","measurementUnit":"clove","displayOrder":2,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/2/medium_square_GARLIC_PEELED_copy.jpg"},{"name":"hickory barbecue spice mix","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"teaspoon","displayOrder":3,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/2422/medium_square_2018-11-29_DS_190219277.jpg"},{"name":"grape tomatoes","quantity":"0.75","measurementUnit":"pint","displayOrder":4,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/191/medium_square_GRAPE_TOMATOES_copy.jpg"},{"name":"gemelli","quantity":"8.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":5,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/2444/medium_square_Gemelli.jpg"},{"name":"lemon","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":6,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/16/medium_square_LEMON_SLICED_1_copy.jpg"},{"name":"basil","quantity":"0.125","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":7,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/5/medium_square_basil-test.jpg"},{"name":"pesto","quantity":"2.0","measurementUnit":"tablespoon","displayOrder":8,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1075/medium_square_PESTO_-4396_copy.jpg"},{"name":"shaved Parmesan cheese","quantity":"2.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":9,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/2328/medium_square_SHAVED_PARM.jpg"},{"name":"8\" aluminum tin","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":10,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/830/medium_square_square_baking_tin.jpg"}],"is_tastemaker":false,"upgradeable":false,"is_holiday_hack":false,"pantry_items":["olive oil","kosher salt","black pepper"],"pantry_items_full":[{"name":"olive oil","quantity":null,"measurementUnit":null,"displayOrder":11,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/267/medium_square_olive-oil-test.jpg"},{"name":"kosher salt","quantity":null,"measurementUnit":null,"displayOrder":12,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/473/medium_square_kosher-salt.jpg"},{"name":"black pepper","quantity":null,"measurementUnit":null,"displayOrder":13,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/493/medium_square_spice-black-pepper-test.jpg"}],"steps":[{"title":"Prepare ingredients","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/base_recipe_step/file/19365/recipe_card_size_FnHA3IsdQ86nf8P3Q1ds_1__Prepare_Ingredients_2P.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003ePreheat oven to 450°F. Bring a large pot of water to a boil over high heat. Wipe \u003cstrong\u003emushrooms\u003c/strong\u003e clean with a damp paper towel (see recipe tip). Trim and discard bottom .25 inch of stem, then cut into .25-inch pieces. Rinse remaining produce. Using the flat side of a knife, gently crush \u003cstrong\u003egarlic cloves\u003c/strong\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Season vegetables","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/base_recipe_step/file/19366/recipe_card_size_31llgk0yStyyJEHmqwai_2__Make_Mushroom_Bacon_2P.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eIn a large bowl, whisk together \u003cstrong\u003ehickory barbecue\u003c/strong\u003e \u003cstrong\u003espice mix\u003c/strong\u003e and \u003cstrong\u003e1 tablespoon olive oil\u003c/strong\u003e, then add \u003cstrong\u003emushrooms \u003c/strong\u003eand toss to coat. Reshape \u003cstrong\u003ealuminum tin\u003c/strong\u003e if bent. Add \u003cstrong\u003ewhole grape\u003c/strong\u003e \u003cstrong\u003etomatoes\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003ecrushed garlic\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003e3 tablespoons olive oil\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003e.25 teaspoon salt\u003c/strong\u003e, and \u003cstrong\u003epepper \u003c/strong\u003eto tin. Toss to combine.\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Roast vegetables ","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/base_recipe_step/file/19367/recipe_card_size_TG6z9MbQu6JsX15QYTg4_3__Roast_Tomatoes_2P.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eSpread \u003cstrong\u003emushrooms\u003c/strong\u003e on 1 half of a baking sheet in a single layer, spacing apart as much as possible. Carefully place \u003cstrong\u003etin\u003c/strong\u003e on other half of baking sheet with mushrooms; transfer to oven and roast until mushrooms are crispy and tomatoes are broken down, 18-20 minutes. \u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Cook pasta","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/base_recipe_step/file/19368/recipe_card_size_uA8jefgdSR27W8tAsSZR_4__Cook_Pasta.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eWhile mushrooms and tomatoes roast, season boiling water generously with \u003cstrong\u003esalt\u003c/strong\u003e. Stir in \u003cstrong\u003egemelli\u003c/strong\u003e and cook until al dente, about 7 minutes. Then, drain and return to pot, off heat. Meanwhile, if you have a zester and want to infuse your pesto with even more flavor, zest \u003cstrong\u003eup to .5 of lemon\u003c/strong\u003e (see recipe tip), then halve. Roughly chop or tear \u003cstrong\u003ebasil\u003c/strong\u003e leaves, discarding stems.\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Mix pesto and finish pasta ","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/base_recipe_step/file/19369/recipe_card_size_1fnbqudIRfGVE3mxQnQy_5__Finish_Pasta_2P.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eIn a small bowl, stir together \u003cstrong\u003epesto\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003elemon zest \u003c/strong\u003e(if using), and \u003cstrong\u003ejuice of .5 lemon \u003c/strong\u003eto combine (use remaining lemon to brighten a glass of water). Once tomatoes are cooked, transfer \u003cstrong\u003eroasted garlic\u003c/strong\u003e to bowl with pesto. Using a fork, gently mash to combine. Transfer \u003cstrong\u003ehalf of tomatoes\u003c/strong\u003e to sheet with mushrooms; set aside for Step 6. Using a spoon, crush \u003cstrong\u003eremaining\u003c/strong\u003e \u003cstrong\u003etomatoes\u003c/strong\u003e in tin, then transfer \u003cstrong\u003ecrushed tomatoes\u003c/strong\u003e \u003cstrong\u003eand juices\u003c/strong\u003e to pot with pasta. Toss to coat.\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Plate roasted tomato pasta","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/base_recipe_step/file/19370/recipe_card_size_wvkeWrHKRSbzkenP0WOA_6__Plate.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eSeason \u003cstrong\u003epasta\u003c/strong\u003e with\u003cstrong\u003e .25 teaspoon salt \u003c/strong\u003eand \u003cstrong\u003epepper \u003c/strong\u003eas desired. Divide \u003cstrong\u003eroasted tomato pasta \u003c/strong\u003ebetween serving bowls. Drizzle over\u003cstrong\u003e lemon pesto\u003c/strong\u003e, then scatter \u003cstrong\u003ewhole\u003c/strong\u003e \u003cstrong\u003eroasted\u003c/strong\u003e \u003cstrong\u003etomatoes\u003c/strong\u003e and \u003cstrong\u003emushroom “bacon”\u003c/strong\u003e  over top. Garnish with \u003cstrong\u003eParmesan\u003c/strong\u003e and \u003cstrong\u003ebasil\u003c/strong\u003e. Enjoy!\u003c/p\u003e"}],"tags":{"all":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"Family-friendly","slug":"family-friendly","hex_color":""}],"allergens":[{"name":"Milk","slug":"milk","hex_color":""},{"name":"Wheat","slug":"wheat","hex_color":""}],"proteins":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"Pasta","slug":"pasta","hex_color":""}],"publicFacing":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"Family-friendly","slug":"family-friendly","hex_color":""}],"feature":[]}}